        <p class="section__label">The beginning</p>
        <h2 class="section__title">A passion born<br>in the snow</h2>
        <p style="font-size:0.97rem;color:var(--gris);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:1.2rem">It all started with a Siberian Husky — Arctic, our first breeding male — who arrived on a January morning in 2015 at our home in Sierre. His ice-blue gaze and untameable energy changed everything.</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.97rem;color:var(--gris);line-height:1.85">Passionate about these strikingly beautiful Nordic breeds, we quickly understood that our mission would be to share this magic with other families — by raising healthy, balanced, loved puppies from their very first breath.</p>
      </div>
